text: Guillermo Gutiérrez (born 8 June 1964) is a Mexican cyclist. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Mexico Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
